Package io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.event

Class DataPacksReloadedEvent

java.lang.Object
net.minecraftforge.eventbus.api.Event
io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.event.DataPacksReloadedEvent
public class DataPacksReloadedEvent extends net.minecraftforge.eventbus.api.Event
Fired on the server after datapacks have been reloaded. This event is fired on the MinecraftForge.EVENT_BUS This event may be fired on the Server Thread, or an async reloader thread. This event is NOT fired on client or on server startup, only after a reload via the reload or the datapack command. This event is not Cancelable and has no Result.
